{"tid":271070,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"行李喼個密碼鎖壞咗點搞","createTime":"2017-06-04T18:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T20:51:14.000Z","uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c55378248e4444740592e387308a4ab9c394e9d2","tid":271070,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"早幾日喺日本飛返嚟，返到屋企至發現個鎖俾人擰過咁款<br />\n仲要試過兩次由000擰到999都開唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無理由咁唔好彩兩次都手快擰過同一個數字架嘛<br />\n於是就上網search有咩方法可以爆鎖啦，試咗以下幾個方法都唔work<br />\n所以想問下大家點搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先個喼係呢種：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.groupon.hk/deals/shopping/elle-aluminium-luggage/719868815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.groupon.hk%2Fdeals%2Fshopping%2Felle-aluminium-luggage%2F719868815&d=vE%2B85aP%2BbIltI3%2BeeYbmCwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=29b932ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.groupon.hk/deals/shopping/elle-aluminium-luggage/719868815</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.grouponcdn.com/deal/9i2w3agJGwUk1gMGnrYB/t620x376/3w-700x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.grouponcdn.com%2Fdeal%2F9i2w3agJGwUk1gMGnrYB%2Ft620x376%2F3w-700x420.jpg&h=e6e99ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係無拉鏈，要閂埋個喼就一定要鎖咁<br />\n因為無拉鏈，上網check啲人話用一字批撳實個拉鏈位嗰啲方法行唔通<br />\n<br />\n跟住再search，啲人話可以靠搵每個轉輪個內輪個凹位再擰三下<br />\n咁我搵到係333啦，都脗合嘅<br />\n因為我本身set咗個密碼係000 (但唔知點解撞000開唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁聽講都可能撞下撞下撞歪咗一兩個數字咁啦<br />\n所以我再試下改一改側邊啲數字，例如111, 101, 099咁樣推一兩格咁樣<br />\n都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就懷疑係個鎖彈開個位已經壞撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/no